            "question": "Are LED lightbars legal?",
            "answer": "<p>Legality depends on color and location. Amber LED lightbars are widely allowed for utility, towing, and construction use, while blue and red light bars are generally restricted to official emergency vehicles. Always confirm your state and local regulations before installing.</p>",
