            "question": "What's the difference between a strobe light bar and a regular lightbar?",
            "answer": "<p>Strobe light bars flash in defined patterns for maximum attention, while a regular lightbar may offer steady illumination or minimal flashing. Most modern LED bars combine both, giving you dozens of selectable patterns in a single unit.</p>",
